# Design system — enforcement contract

**Replaces:** `design-system-enforcement.mdc`, `design-system-docs-enforcement.mdc`, `material-semantics.mdc`, `figma-code-connect-workflow.mdc`
**CI:** `pnpm lint` → `scripts/check-design-contract.mjs`

---

## Token contract

- Import aliases from **`#lib/design-system`**: `ui.radius`, `ui.padding`, `ui.gap`, `ui.elevation`, `ui.tone`, `ui.priority`, `uiRadius`, `uiSurfaceElevation`, `uiDensity`, `uiSurfaceInset`, `buttonVariantSchema`, `badgeVariantSchema`, etc.
- **Forbidden geometry:** `rounded-3xl`, `rounded-4xl`, `shadow-2xl`, arbitrary `rounded-[…]`.
- **Spacing:** Tailwind scale, `p-surface-*`, `gap-surface-*`, `gap-density-*`. Forbidden: arbitrary literals (`p-[12px]`, `gap-[7px]`). CSS-variable refs (`var(--…)`) remain allowed.
- **`@theme inline` in `app/globals.css`** must only reference `var(--*)` names that exist under `:root`/`.dark` (enforced by `check-design-contract.mjs`).

## Semantic color contract

- Consume: `bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, etc.
- **Primitive hovers:** use `bg-primary-hover` / `bg-secondary-hover` — **not** `hover:bg-primary/…` or `hover:bg-secondary/…`.
- No hardcoded hex values in components.

## Primitive import contract

- UI shelf: **`components/ui/**`** on disk.
- **All consumers** (`app/**`, `components/**` except the shelf, `hooks/**`, `lib/**`) import via **`#components/ui/<primitive>`** only.
- Forbidden outside `components/ui` (ESLint):
  - `@radix-ui/*`, `radix-ui`, `@base-ui/react`
  - filesystem-relative `**/components/ui` import specifiers

## Runtime validation

When variants/sizes come from external sources (CMS, query params, API), parse with schemas:

```ts
import { buttonVariantSchema, uiPrimitiveSchema, parseUiSurfaceSpaceKey } from "#lib/design-system"
buttonVariantSchema.parse(value)
```

