## Documentation sync (`docs/design-system/**/*.md`)

- **Code is truth:** `app/globals.css`, `lib/design-system.ts`, `components/ui/`. Docs describe what code implements.
- Do not document tokens, variant strings, or APIs not yet in code.
- When token/primitive APIs change, update `docs/design-system/governance.md` and Code Connect templates in the same change.

## Figma Code Connect

- Run `pnpm design:check` before adding new primitives to verify Figma variant parity.
- Do not add semantic tokens to Figma without implementing them in `app/globals.css` first.
- Primitive: `data-slot` attributes must match Code Connect variant mapping.
